          <p class="ba-sub">For businesses that want free backlink reports — anchor text, referring domains, lost links — without paying for Ahrefs.</p>
        </div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">Bing Webmaster Tools is the most underrated tool on this list. It's the only completely free option with real backlink analysis: anchor text distribution, referring domain counts, and lost link tracking. It also added AI Performance tracking in 2025-2026, showing how your site appears in Copilot and Bing AI results. Import your Google Search Console data directly to get started in minutes. Bing represents ~10% of US search, so treat the data as supplemental to GSC — but the backlink reports are uniquely valuable at $0.</p>
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Only free tool with real backlink analysis</h4><p>Anchor text, referring domains, lost links — at the level you'd expect from a paid tool. Fully free.</p></div></li>
