          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Import Google Search Console data directly</h4><p>Start with your existing GSC property data — no re-verification required.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✗</span><div><h4>Honest limitation: Bing is ~10% of US search volume</h4><p>Rankings and performance data reflect Bing's smaller index. Google-first businesses should treat BWT as supplemental, not primary.</p></div></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- #10 AlsoAsked -->
