        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">AlsoAsked maps the "People Also Ask" boxes from Google results, showing question trees and parent-child relationships. If you search "HVAC maintenance," it shows the questions Google groups under that topic — and the sub-questions under each of those. Saves hours of manual PAA research. Limited to 3 free searches per day and paid plan required for export ($12.50/mo minimum), but for planning FAQ sections it's genuinely useful.</p>
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Reveals exact questions Google associates with your keywords</h4><p>Not what you think people ask — what Google's data shows they actually ask. Different and more reliable.</p></div></li>
